{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"interiorPolygons"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The area occupied by any interior polygons is excluded from the overall shape."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Interior polygons should not overlap. An interior polygon should not have"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interior polygons of its own."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If there are no interior polygons, the value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon\/interiorpolygons"]}],"metadata":{"title":"interiorPolygons","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"interiorPolygons","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNPolygon(py)interiorPolygons","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"interiorPolygons"}],"role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon\/interiorPolygons","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Th